<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>{{artist.name}} - 아티스트 상세</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/artiststyle.css">
</head>
<body>
<header>
    <h1>DMU Sound - 아티스트 상세</h1>
</header>

<main>
    <section class="artist-info">
        <h2>{{artist.name}}</h2>
        <img src="{{artist.imageUrl}}" alt="{{artist.name}}" class="artist-image" width="300">
    </section>

    <section class="top-tracks">
        <h3>🎵 Top 10 Tracks</h3>
        <ul class="top-track-list">
            {{#topTracks}}
                <li class="top-track-item">
                    <img src="{{imageUrl}}" alt="{{trackName}}" width="50" height="50">
                    <a href="/track/{{id}}">{{trackName}}</a> -
                    {{albumName}}
                </li>
            {{/topTracks}}
            {{^topTracks}}
                <li>Top 트랙 정보를 불러올 수 없습니다.</li>
            {{/topTracks}}
        </ul>
    </section>
</main>
</body>
</html>
